---
import CaseStudy from '../../layouts/CaseStudy.astro';
---
<CaseStudy slug="sigil">
  <Fragment slot="meta">
    <div class="cs-meta-card">
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Client</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Pine Island Games</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Product</div><div class="cs-meta-value">SIGIL</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Duration</div><div class="cs-meta-value">2022–2023</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Role</div><div class="cs-meta-value">Creative Director (Brand Identity &amp; Product Design)</div></div>
      <div class="cs-meta-row"><div class="cs-meta-label">Launch</div><div class="cs-meta-value">May 2023 Kickstarter</div></div>
    </div>
  </Fragment>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="stat-strip">
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">$22K+</div><div class="stat-label">Kickstarter funded</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">303%</div><div class="stat-label">Of $7,500 goal</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">347</div><div class="stat-label">Backers</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Context · Action · Result</div>
    <div class="car-grid">
      <div class="car-sidebar">
        <div class="car-step active" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-sigil-1')"><div class="car-step-label">01 · Context</div><div class="car-step-title">The situation</div></div>
        <div class="car-step" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-sigil-2')"><div class="car-step-label">02 · Action</div><div class="car-step-title">What I did</div></div>
        <div class="car-step" onclick="switchCar(this,'car-sigil-3')"><div class="car-step-label">03 · Result</div><div class="car-step-title">What it produced</div></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div id="car-sigil-1" class="car-content">
          <div class="car-content-label">01 · Context</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">A strong game system with no commercial wrapper.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">SIGIL is a two-player abstract strategy dueling game designed by Andreas Voellmer, a former Magic: The Gathering pro tour competitor. Pine Island Games founder Jasper Burch had developed the core mechanics over nearly 15 years, but the product had no visual identity, no board system, and no production-ready assets.<br /><br />Burch brought me on to build the full visual and physical product layer — translating a mechanically complete game into something that could be understood, manufactured, and sold.</div>
        </div>
        <div id="car-sigil-2" class="car-content" style="display:none">
          <div class="car-content-label">02 · Action</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">Built the brand, the board, and the product system.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">Built the SIGIL visual identity from the ground up — including logo, typography, color system, and overall visual language rooted in arcane and celestial themes. The Latin inscription ringing the board reinforces the game's mystical positioning.<br /><br />Designed the circular game board, including the nine spell zones, node pathways, and stone placement system. The challenge was translating abstract gameplay mechanics — surrounding, casting, and control — into a layout players could immediately understand.<br /><br />Developed the physical product system, including packaging, dice design, component pouches, and branded elements. Created production-ready files for manufacturing to ensure consistency across all components.<br /><br />Advised on illustrator selection for spell artwork and provided creative direction to ensure visual consistency across all commissioned assets.</div>
        </div>
        <div id="car-sigil-3" class="car-content" style="display:none">
          <div class="car-content-label">03 · Result</div>
          <div class="car-content-title">Funded, manufactured, shipped.</div>
          <div class="car-content-body">SIGIL launched on Kickstarter in May 2023 and funded at 303% of its $7,500 goal, raising $22,740 from 347 backers.<br /><br />The visual and product system I developed is the version that was manufactured and shipped to customers.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">What this proves</div>
    <div class="foundation-card">
      <div class="foundation-section-title">Translating mechanics into product.</div>
      <div class="foundation-desc" style="margin-bottom:0">A strong system isn't enough — it has to be legible, intuitive, and physically executable. This project demonstrates how visual design and production thinking turn an abstract concept into a real, manufacturable product.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Promo</div>
    <div class="media-video">
      <video src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-teaser-promo.mp4" controls playsinline preload="metadata"></video>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Brand System</div>
    <div class="sigil-logo-wrap">
      <div class="sigil-logo-cell sigil-logo-cell-logo">
        <img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-3d-logo.png" alt="SIGIL 3D rendered logo" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="sigil-logo-cell sigil-logo-cell-icon">
        <img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-3d-icon.png" alt="SIGIL 3D rendered icon" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="brand-system" style="margin-top:14px">
      <div class="brand-swatches">
        <div class="brand-swatch">
          <div class="swatch-chip" style="background:#442554"></div>
          <div class="swatch-name">Dark Foundation</div>
          <div class="swatch-meta">CMYK 80/94/36/32</div>
          <div class="swatch-meta">HEX #442554</div>
          <div class="swatch-meta">RGB 68 · 37 · 84</div>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-swatch">
          <div class="swatch-chip" style="background:#EF3E32"></div>
          <div class="swatch-name">Sigil Red</div>
          <div class="swatch-meta">HEX #EF3E32</div>
          <div class="swatch-meta">RGB 239 · 62 · 50</div>
          <div class="swatch-meta">CMYK 0 · 91 · 87 · 0</div>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-swatch">
          <div class="swatch-chip" style="background:#3658A8"></div>
          <div class="swatch-name">Arcane Blue</div>
          <div class="swatch-meta">HEX #3658A8</div>
          <div class="swatch-meta">RGB 54 · 88 · 168</div>
          <div class="swatch-meta">CMYK 88 · 73 · 0 · 0</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="brand-type">
        <div class="type-row">
          <div class="type-meta">
            <div class="type-name">1651 Alchemy</div>
            <div class="type-role">Primary display</div>
          </div>
          <div class="type-sample type-sample-display">ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ<br />abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz<br />1234567890</div>
        </div>
        <div class="type-row">
          <div class="type-meta">
            <div class="type-name">1651 Alchemy Italic</div>
            <div class="type-role">Secondary display</div>
          </div>
          <div class="type-sample type-sample-display-italic">ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ<br />abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz<br />1234567890</div>
        </div>
        <div class="type-row">
          <div class="type-meta">
            <div class="type-name">Ten Oldstyle Medium</div>
            <div class="type-role">Body / supporting</div>
          </div>
          <div class="type-sample type-sample-oldstyle">ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ<br />abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz<br />1234567890</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Product System</div>
    <div class="sigil-product-stack">
      <div class="sigil-grid-2x2">
        <figure class="media-figure">
          <img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-ux-layout.webp" alt="SIGIL board UX layout" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="media-caption">Board UX layout — information architecture</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="media-figure">
          <img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-3d-board.webp" alt="Final SIGIL board with spell zones and pieces" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="media-caption">Final board with spell zones and pieces</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="sigil-spell-stack">
        <img class="spell-back" src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-spell-5stone.png" alt="SIGIL Starfall spell, 5-stone" loading="lazy" />
        <img class="spell-mid" src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-spell-3stone.png" alt="SIGIL Fireblast spell, 3-stone" loading="lazy" />
        <img class="spell-front" src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-spell-1stone.png" alt="SIGIL Comet spell, 1-stone" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="sigil-grid-2x2">
        <figure class="media-figure">
          <img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-box-front.webp" alt="SIGIL box dieline" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="media-caption">Box dieline — production-ready flat layout</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="media-figure">
          <img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-box-back.webp" alt="SIGIL box back panel" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="media-caption">Box back — Graphics Designed by Michael Hnath</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div class="sigil-grid-2x2">
        <figure class="media-figure">
          <img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-box.webp" alt="SIGIL production box" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="media-caption">Production box</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="media-figure">
          <img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-delux-box.webp" alt="SIGIL collector's edition box" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="media-caption">Collector's edition</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">In Play</div>
    <div class="sigil-carousel" data-sigil-carousel>
      <div class="sigil-carousel-main">
        <button class="sigil-carousel-arrow prev" type="button" aria-label="Previous slide" data-sigil-prev>‹</button>
        <div class="sigil-carousel-track" data-sigil-track>
          <div class="sigil-carousel-slide active"><img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-lifestyle-boardsetup.webp" alt="Board mid-setup" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="sigil-carousel-slide"><img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-lifestyle-stonecloseup.webp" alt="SIGIL stones close-up" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="sigil-carousel-slide"><img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-lifestyle-bothplayers.webp" alt="Two players mid-game" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="sigil-carousel-slide"><img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-lifestyle-game-move.webp" alt="Player executing a move" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="sigil-carousel-slide"><img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-lifestyle-skyview.webp" alt="Overhead board view" loading="lazy" /></div>
        </div>
        <button class="sigil-carousel-arrow next" type="button" aria-label="Next slide" data-sigil-next>›</button>
      </div>
      <div class="sigil-carousel-thumbs">
        <button class="sigil-thumb active" type="button" data-sigil-index="0" aria-label="Show slide 1"><img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-lifestyle-boardsetup.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" /></button>
        <button class="sigil-thumb" type="button" data-sigil-index="1" aria-label="Show slide 2"><img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-lifestyle-stonecloseup.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" /></button>
        <button class="sigil-thumb" type="button" data-sigil-index="2" aria-label="Show slide 3"><img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-lifestyle-bothplayers.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" /></button>
        <button class="sigil-thumb" type="button" data-sigil-index="3" aria-label="Show slide 4"><img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-lifestyle-game-move.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" /></button>
        <button class="sigil-thumb" type="button" data-sigil-index="4" aria-label="Show slide 5"><img src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-lifestyle-skyview.webp" alt="" loading="lazy" /></button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Kickstarter</div>
    <div class="phone-mockup">
      <iframe class="phone-iframe" src="/Personal/Images/Sigil/sigil-kickstarter-phone-mockup.html" title="SIGIL Kickstarter campaign page mockup" loading="lazy" scrolling="no"></iframe>
      <div class="phone-caption">Campaign page design — brand system applied by Pine Island Games team</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</CaseStudy>

<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,500;0,600;0,700;1,500;1,600;1,700&display=swap');

  @font-face{
    font-family:'1651 Alchemy';
    src:url('/Personal/Images/Sigil/1651%20Alchemy%20W00%20Normal.ttf') format('truetype');
    font-weight:normal;
    font-style:normal;
    font-display:swap;
  }
  @font-face{
    font-family:'1651 Alchemy';
    src:url('/Personal/Images/Sigil/1651%20Alchemy%20W00%20Italic.ttf') format('truetype');
    font-weight:normal;
    font-style:italic;
    font-display:swap;
  }

  .sigil-logo-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:14px;align-items:stretch}
  .sigil-logo-cell{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:#442554;border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:32px}
  :root[data-theme="dark"] .sigil-logo-cell{background:var(--bg2)}
  .sigil-logo-cell img{width:100%;height:auto;display:block}
  .sigil-logo-cell-logo{grid-column:span 3}
  .sigil-logo-cell-icon{grid-column:span 1}
  @media (max-width:640px){
    .sigil-logo-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:12px}
    .sigil-logo-cell-logo,.sigil-logo-cell-icon{grid-column:auto}
    .sigil-logo-cell-icon img{max-width:50%;margin:0 auto}
  }

  .brand-system{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r-lg);padding:28px}
  .brand-swatches{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:8px}
  .brand-swatch{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:2px}
  .swatch-chip{width:100%;aspect-ratio:3/2;max-width:160px;border-radius:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:6px}
  .swatch-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-top:4px}
  .swatch-meta{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:.04em}

  .brand-type{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:24px}
  .type-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(140px,180px) minmax(0,1fr);gap:20px;align-items:baseline;padding:14px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
  .type-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;padding-bottom:0}
  .type-meta{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px}
  .type-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text)}
  .type-role{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--text3)}
  .type-sample{font-size:18px;line-height:1.3;color:var(--text);word-break:break-word}
  .type-sample-display{font-family:'1651 Alchemy','Playfair Display',serif;font-weight:normal;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:.01em}
  .type-sample-display-italic{font-family:'1651 Alchemy','Playfair Display',serif;font-weight:normal;font-style:italic;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:.01em}
  .type-sample-oldstyle{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-weight:500;font-size:20px}

  .sigil-product-stack{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px}
  .sigil-grid-2x2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));grid-auto-rows:1fr;gap:14px}
  .sigil-grid-2x2 .media-figure{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  .sigil-grid-2x2 .media-figure img{width:100%;height:auto;aspect-ratio:1/1;object-fit:cover;flex:1}

  .sigil-spell-stack{position:relative;background:var(--bg2);border-radius:var(--r-lg);aspect-ratio:2/1;overflow:hidden}
  .sigil-spell-stack img{position:absolute;top:8%;height:84%;width:auto;aspect-ratio:1/1;object-fit:contain;filter:drop-shadow(0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.32))}
  .sigil-spell-stack .spell-back{left:8%;z-index:1}
  .sigil-spell-stack .spell-mid{left:29%;z-index:2}
  .sigil-spell-stack .spell-front{left:50%;z-index:3}

  .sigil-carousel{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
  .sigil-carousel-main{position:relative;background:var(--bg2);border-radius:var(--r-lg);overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:16/10}
  .sigil-carousel-track{position:relative;width:100%;height:100%}
  .sigil-carousel-slide{position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:0;transition:opacity 220ms ease;pointer-events:none}
  .sigil-carousel-slide.active{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto}
  .sigil-carousel-slide img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block}
  .sigil-carousel-arrow{position:absolute;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-size:22px;line-height:1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;z-index:2;transition:background var(--transition),border-color var(--transition);padding:0}
  .sigil-carousel-arrow:hover{background:var(--bg2);border-color:var(--border2)}
  .sigil-carousel-arrow.prev{left:10px}
  .sigil-carousel-arrow.next{right:10px}
  .sigil-carousel-thumbs{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,minmax(0,1fr));gap:8px}
  .sigil-thumb{padding:0;background:var(--bg2);border:2px solid transparent;border-radius:var(--r);overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;aspect-ratio:1/1;opacity:.55;transition:border-color var(--transition),opacity var(--transition)}
  .sigil-thumb:hover{opacity:.85}
  .sigil-thumb.active{border-color:var(--text);opacity:1}
  .sigil-thumb img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block}

  .phone-mockup{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:28px}
  .phone-iframe{width:100%;max-width:480px;height:840px;border:0;background:transparent;display:block;color-scheme:light}
  .phone-caption{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase}

  @media (max-width:640px){
    .brand-swatches{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:6px}
    .swatch-chip{max-width:100%}
    .type-row{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:6px}
    .sigil-grid-2x2{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .sigil-carousel-main{aspect-ratio:4/3}
    .sigil-carousel-thumbs{grid-template-columns:repeat(5,minmax(0,1fr));gap:6px}
  }
</style>
